    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="F431A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If I may have it, when it's<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 dead,</l>
                    <l>I'll be contented - so - </l>
                    <l>If just as soon as Breath<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 is out </l>
                    <l>It shall belong to me - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Until they lock it in the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Grave,</l>
                    <l>'Tis<add type="alternate" extent="Bliss I cannot weigh -">Wealth I cannot weigh. &amp;#x2022; Right [I cannot weigh.]</add>
 Bliss I cannot weigh - </l>
                    <l>For tho' they lock Thee in<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the Grave, </l>
                    <l>Myself - can<add type="alternate" extent="own">hold</add>
 own the key - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Think of it Lover! I and Thee </l>
                    <l>Permitted - face to face to be -</l>
                    <l>After a Life - a Death -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 we'll say - </l>
                    <l>For Death was That - </l>
                    <l>And This - is Thee -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I'll tell Thee All - how<add type="alternate" extent="Bald">Blank -</add>
 Bald<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 it grew - </l>
                    <l>How Midnight felt, at first -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to me -</l>
                    <l>How all the Clocks stopped<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 in the World - </l>
                    <l>And Sunshine pinched me -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 'Twas so cold - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Then how the Grief got sleepy -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 some - </l>
                    <l>As if my soul were deaf and<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 dumb - </l>
                    <l>Just making signs -<add type="alternate" extent="across">it seemed</add>
 across -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to Thee -</l>
                    <l>That this way - thou could'st<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
<add type="alternate" extent="notice">speak to -</add>
 notice me - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I'll tell you how I tried to keep </l>
                    <l>A smile, to show you, when<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 this Deep<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>All Waded - We look back<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 for Play, </l>
                    <l>At those Old Times - in Calvary.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Forgive me, if the Grave<add type="alternate" extent="come">seem</add>
 come<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 slow - </l>
                    <l>For<add type="alternate" extent="Coveting">eagerness -</add>
 Coveting to look at Thee - </l>
                    <l>Forgive me, if to<add type="alternate" extent="stroke">touch &amp;#x2022; greet</add>
 stroke<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 thy frost </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="Outvisions">[Out]fables -</add>
Outvisions Paradise!  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
